OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1771854452
OL,3,CSurrey Police makes 'significant
OL,4,Cprogress' in responding to incidents
OL,5,Cand calls
OL,7,FConcerns about how Surrey Police
OL,8,Fresponds to incidents and calls from
OL,9,Fthe public have been lifted by His
OL,10,FMajesty's Inspectorate of Constabulary
OL,11,Fand Fire and Rescue Services (HMICFRS).
OL,13,FThis is related to improvements needed
OL,14,Ffollowing an inspection in December
OL,15,F2023. HMICFRS has informed the force
OL,16,Fthat the causes of concern it
OL,17,Fpreviously raised have now been
OL,18,Faddressed and closed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
