FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1771854452
OL,3,CSurrey Police makes 'significant
OL,4,Cprogress' in responding to incidents
OL,5,Cand calls
OL,7,FSurrey Police says non-emergency calls
OL,8,Fare now answered three minutes faster
OL,9,Fthan a year ago, and it now takes, on
OL,10,Faverage, 12 seconds to answer a 101
OL,11,Fcall, which is down from 3.4 minutes
OL,12,Fin December 2024.
OL,14,F101 call abandonment rates have
OL,15,Fdropped dramatically from 36% to 7%,
OL,16,Fand 999 calls are now answered in two
OL,17,Fseconds rather than five, with the
OL,18,Fcall abandonment rate reduced to 2%.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1771854452
OL,3,CSurrey Police makes 'significant
OL,4,Cprogress' in responding to incidents
OL,5,Cand calls
OL,7,FThe previously separate Force Control
OL,8,FRoom and Contact Centre were merged
OL,9,Finto the Force Command Centre, working
OL,10,Fout of the same location.
OL,12,FA new call grading system for triaging
OL,13,Fand responding to calls was also
OL,14,Fimplemented, and on average, officers
OL,15,Fattend the most serious calls within
OL,16,F13 minutes, faster than the agreed 20-
OL,17,Fminute standard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1771854452
OL,3,CSurrey Police makes 'significant
OL,4,Cprogress' in responding to incidents
OL,5,Cand calls
OL,7,FAssistant Chief Constable Sarah
OL,8,FGrahame said: "Serving the public is
OL,9,Fat the heart of everything we do. When
OL,10,Fthe causes of concern were first
OL,11,Fraised, we were clear about what they
OL,12,Fmeant. They told us that we weren't
OL,13,Falways delivering the level of service
OL,14,Fthe public should rightly expect.
OL,16,F"These reforms have led to real
OL,17,Fimprovements for the people we serve,
OL,18,Fand they are improvements that every
OL,19,Fmember of Surrey Police has
OL,20,Fcontributed to."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1771854452
OL,3,CSurrey Police makes 'significant
OL,4,Cprogress' in responding to incidents
OL,5,Cand calls
OL,7,FThe force says its responsibility is
OL,8,Fnow to "maintain" this level of
OL,9,Fservice.
OL,11,FSarah Grahame continued: "These are
OL,12,Fnot just statistics. They represent
OL,13,Freal people receiving help more
OL,14,Fquickly; victims feeling heard;
OL,15,Fvulnerable individuals getting a
OL,16,Ftimely response; and communities
OL,17,Fgaining confidence in their local
OL,18,Fpolice.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1771854452
OL,3,CSurrey Police makes 'significant
OL,4,Cprogress' in responding to incidents
OL,5,Cand calls
OL,7,F"Having the causes of concern lifted
OL,8,Fis a significant achievement, but it
OL,9,Fis not the end of the journey. The
OL,10,Fpublic's expectations continue to
OL,11,Frise, and so do ours. Our
OL,12,Fresponsibility now is to maintain this
OL,13,Flevel of service, continue to learn,
OL,14,Fand keep improving."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1771854452
OL,3,CSurrey Police makes 'significant
OL,4,Cprogress' in responding to incidents
OL,5,Cand calls
OL,7,FHis Majesty's Inspector of
OL,8,FConstabulary Inspector Roy Wilsher,
OL,9,Fwho has responsibility for Surrey
OL,10,FPolice, said: "I am pleased that
OL,11,FSurrey Police has made significant
OL,12,Fprogress in these areas since we
OL,13,Fraised these causes of concern."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
